Description.Text: This is an excellent, modern deluxe hotel. The leisure facilities are state of the art with a large pool, gymnasium and exercise studios. (09/05/MJ)

Located opposite Cadogan Gardens, just off of Sloane Street in the heart of Knightsbridge. The hotel is situated a few minutes walk from Harrods, Harvey Nichols and many designer stores such as Chanel, Armani and Gucci.

The majority of the rooms have been recently refurbished to an excellent standard. All rooms have been painted cream in colour with dark wood furniture. All have mini bar, Bose CD player and trouser press. The bathrooms are of a very high standard with marble flooring and white walls.
It is a modern building consisting of two towers. The first is 18 floors high, the second is 12 floors high. The top floor of the hotel affords amazing views over London.

The hotel has several restaurants. There is a health food restaurant attached to the gym, serving snacks and fruit juices, the lounge restaurant area, an Italian restaurant and the famous Rib Room and Oyster Bar.

The lobby is medium in size. The lobby is decorated in pale creams and marbles with comfortable sofas. It leads directly into the open plan lounge/informal dining area where guests can take breakfast, lunch and light snacks all day.
